    "OrangeGrisetteDescription": "A bright, edible mushroom. Its colors can range from pale yellow to dark orange. Edible.",

    "WaningMoonShroomDisplayName": "Waning Moon Shroom",
    "WaningMoonShroomDescription": "And sometimes, trying your best is not enough and you hate having to deal with it. This mushroom is likely inedible.",

    "SulfurTuftDisplayName": "Sulfur Tuft",
    "SulfurTuftDescription": "This mushroom is bitter and poisonous; consuming it can cause vomiting, diarrhea and convulsions. Do not confuse it with the edible brick cap!",

    "ParasolMushroomDisplayName": "Parasol Mushroom",
    "ParasolMushroomDescription": "A great tasting, easy to identify mushroom that is large enough to spot from afar. When young this mushroom looks very similar to some of the deadly amanitas.",

    "BleedingHeartDisplayName": "Bleeding Heart",
    "BleedingHeartDescription": "Remember the dreams you had? Hold onto them too tightly and you might bleed just like this mushroom when you squeeze it. Highly poisonous.",

    "MM_AllEyes.DisplayName": "All Eyes",
    "MM_AllEyes.Description": "You could have sworn those eyes were following your movements. Eating this mushroom causes one to lose their sight as well as hallucinations.",

    "MM_BleedingToothFungus.DisplayName": "Bleeding Tooth Fungus",
"MM_BleedingToothFungus.Description": "This mushroom is not known to be poisonous, but it isn't particularly edible due to its foul taste. This acrid taste persists even in dried specimens.",

"MM_BurgerShroom.DisplayName": "Burger Shroom",
"MM_BurgerShroom.Description": "A mushroom that suspiciously looks, smells and tastes like a burger.",

"MM_Deathcap.DisplayName": "Deathcap",
"MM_Deathcap.Description": "An innocuous looking mushroom that is among the most poisonous along with the Destroying Angel. The main poison, alpha-amanitin, kills liver cells and passes through the kidneys to be recirculated and cause more damage.",
    
"MM_GreyKnight.DisplayName": "The Grey Knight",
