"MM_Champignon.DisplayName": "Champignon",
"MM_Champignon.Description": "Agaricus bisporus, commonly known as the cultivated mushroom. Usually referring to the whole genus 'Agaricus', 'Champignon' is also used to refer to the common 'button' mushroom you can get anywhere.",

"MM_Aspen.DisplayName": "Aspen",
"MM_Aspen.Description": "A very solid and quite tall bolete with a distinctive orange coloured cap and and a pale stem. Needs thorough cooking.",

